<secondary-navigation-message>
    <secondary-navigation-message-title>
        Why Is Patagonia Making Food?
    </secondary-navigation-message-title>
    <secondary-navigation-message-body>

        <p class=3D"title-5 mb-1">Why Is Patagonia Making Food?</p>
        <p class=3D"p p-xs mb-2">
            Yvon Chouinard shares his motivation for starting Patagonia Pro=
visions, and why it=E2=80=99s important to offer delicious, nutritious food=
s that restore, rather than deplete, our planet.</p>
            <p class=3D"title-5"><a href=3D"https://www.patagonia.com/stori=
es/provisions/learn/why-food/story-168527.html" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"=
btn btn-xs cta-link cta-link-underline" rel=3D"noopener">Learn Why</a></p>
    </secondary-navigation-message-body>
</secondary-navigation-message>
<secondary-navigation-message>
    <secondary-navigation-message-title>
        Free Shipping on Orders Over $99
    </secondary-navigation-message-title>
    <secondary-navigation-message-body>
        <p class=3D"title-5 mb-1">Free Shipping on Orders Over&nbsp;$99</p>
            <p class=3D"p p-xs mb-2">Orders are shipped within 1-2 business=
 days and arrive within 3-10 business days. Need it sooner? Concerned about=
 the environmental impact? Flexible shipping options are available.</p>
            <p class=3D"title-5"><a href=3D"https://www.patagonia.com/shipp=
ing-information.html" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"btn btn-xs cta-link cta-li=
nk-underline" rel=3D"noopener">More Details</a></p>
    </secondary-navigation-message-body>
</secondary-navigation-message>
<secondary-navigation-message>
    <secondary-navigation-message-title>
        Earth Is Now Our Only Shareholder
    </secondary-navigation-message-title>
    <secondary-navigation-message-body>
        <p class=3D"title-5 mb-1">Earth Is Now Our Only Shareholder</p>
            <p class=3D"p p-xs mb-2">If we have any hope of a thriving plan=
et=E2=80=94much less a business=E2=80=94it is going to take all of us doing=
 what we can with the resources we have. This is what we can do.</p>
            <p class=3D"title-5"><a href=3D"https://www.patagonia.com/owner=
ship/" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"btn btn-xs cta-link cta-link-underline" r=
el=3D"noopener">Read Yvon=E2=80=99s Letter</a></p>
   </secondary-navigation-message-body>
</secondary-navigation-message>
